colcon build (arguments:)
--packages-up-to - build packages you want
--packages-select  - for single package
--symlink-install - automatic sync of noncompilable code
--event-handlers console_direct+ - show whole log in console

(interface possibilities)
https://docs.ros.org/en/humble/Concepts/Basic/About-Interfaces.html

(manage ros objects)
rqt


(visualize topics)
rqt_graph

ros2 run rqt_console rqt_console

ros2 bag record $topic_name
ros2 bag record -o subset $topic_name1 $topic_name2

(example pkg creation:)
ros2 pkg create --build-type ament_cmake --license Apache-2.0 <package_name> --dependencies rclpy 

(find whether package_name is sufficient for depends: (<distro>/distribution.yaml)
https://github.com/ros/rosdistro

